Package parser

Class CodeLine

java.lang.Object
parser.CodeLine
public class CodeLine
extends java.lang.Object
A CodeLine stands for LC-3 Text Line. It contains the line number, full text of a single line and other attributes of the parsed line.
Author:
wilber

      Constructor.
      Parameters:
      fullText - Full string text of the line.
      comm - String command of the line or null
      label - Line's label (as in "LABEL: COMMAND")
      targetLabel - Label the line points to
      jump - Whether the command is a jump/break command
      registers - Registers used by this line
      line - Line index
